text: Tarrazú is the name of the 5th canton of San José Province in Costa Rica. The canton has an area of 297.50 km².Instituto Geográfico Nacional (IGN), 2001. ==Districts== The canton of Tarrazú is divided in three districts (distritos): # San Marcos # San Lorenzo # San Carlos ==References== Category:San José Province Category:Cantons of Costa Rica Category:1868 establishments in North America Category:19th-century establishments in Costa Rica
